    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels at MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per the credibility plan for a Class II device at MRL 2. The CFD model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under CPB conditions. The relative hemolysis index criterion (RH < 1) is satisfied across all five evaluated operating points.",
